<li>Introduction The L-arabinose operon of Escherichia coli is both positively and negatively regulated by AraC protein ( for a review , see Schleif , 1987 ) .	[<a href="https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/?term=1560456" target="_blank">1560456</a>]<br></li>
