<li>SoxS is a member of the AraC subfamily of helix-turn-helix proteins ( 1 , 13 , 41 ) .	[<a href="https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/?term=7896696" target="_blank">7896696</a>]<br></li>
