<li>l-kDa SoxR protein bears significant homology only to the MerR family of proteins among known sequences , while the 12.9-kDa SoxS protein is related to the family of bacterial gene regulators exemplified by AraC .	[<a href="https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/?term=1653416" target="_blank">1653416</a>]<br></li>
